{"tid":1571621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「發夢山撚」求生地圖","createTime":"2019-09-15T13:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T16:14:53.000Z","uid":69334,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"163ef5c51cbe0cc2b5b106a5efa2ec4f3635e987","tid":1571621,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"岩先見到有手足發夢上左山蕩失路，所以想分享個用左好耐既行山地圖比手足。<br />\n<br />\n識玩依個綠野遊蹤，上左山都無咁易比野狗襲擊，因為佢有好多路連政府都無record。download左個app之後，最緊要去離線地圖download番Hong Kong V4 multi lingual map, load番就攪掂架喇。<br />\n<br />\n依個app救過小弟行山好多次，相信手足夢遊左上山都會救到你一命。有顏色highlight左既係郊遊徑，無行山經驗既都可以handle到。灰色同啡色既，短短地可以行，太長既話不建議。<br />\n<br />\n不過只限android<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mountain.tracks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.mountain.tracks&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e24e3fe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mountain.tracks</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ErOLr2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErOLr2x.jpg&h=596770f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCaFfVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCaFfVU.jpg&h=bb2caeef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJww62y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJww62y.jpg&h=59dbc711&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dacc5ce4880a4a969ee8b8649fb9075e4ef428a","tid":1571621,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"開啟新戰線：「天滅中共 平反六四」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/